%    2.04 |         | .55      .95     | JT:    Corn   http://www.sopra   sa.com/index2.htm 
%    2.05 |         | .51662   .99191  | JT:    http://www.sopra   sa.com/index2.htm
%    2.06 |         | .4       .85     | Guillaume sat
